description:
Signatures: *⁴ A-4X⁴.
Translation of: Imago primi saeculi Societatis Iesu.
Work of Joannes Bollandus and Godefridus Henschenius, but has been ascribed to Jean de Tollenaer. Translated by Laurent Uwens. Poems largely by Adrien Poirters.
Title engraved by M. Natalis after A. van Diepenbeek; 104 emblematic engravings within ornamental borders by Cornelis Galle.
Electronic reproduction.
